Desktop -> Hot Corners:
- Top Left: Show Applications Menu
- Top Right: Maximize Current Window
- Bottom Left: Multitasking View
- Bottom Right: Minimize Current Window

Power: Set all buttons to hibernate.
Mouse & Touchpad: (Touchpad) Tap to click.

Tweaks -> Applications ->
- Files: Turn OFF single click.
- Terminal: Opacity to 90%.

User Accounts:
- Set profile photo. :)
- Turn OFF Guest Account!

Note: ffmpeg not tested!



### DESKTOP SPECIFIC ###

Tweaks -> Appearance:
- Window Controls: Minimize Right

Note: Bluetooth will not be automatically disabled on a desktop.



### LAPTOP SPECIFIC ###

Note: Power settings will not be configured properly!
